section: rts
synopsis: Fix "unknown/strange object 24 crash" in compacting GC
issues: #27434
mrs: !16261

description {
Fix a crash in the compacting garbage collector when collecting large
function-application thunks. Affected programs crashed with an internal error
of the form "update_fwd_large: unknown/strange object 24" when run with the
compacting GC (``+RTS -c``).
}
